title: Lost Civilizations, Part 3: European Visitors to the New World Before Columbus
description: Learn about cultures that came to America long before Columbus, suggesting that trans-oceanic voyages could be accomplished well back into the Bronze Age.
itunes:author: Scott Rank, PhD
